Package: orca-os
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, python3-venv, systemd, curl
Maintainer: Orca OS Team <team@orca-os.dev>
Description: AI-Powered Linux Operating System
 Orca OS is an AI-powered operating system that provides natural language
 interaction with your Linux system. It includes:
 .
  * Natural language command translation
  * AI-powered system management
  * Safe command execution with validation
  * Background daemon service
  * REST API for integration
 .
 This package provides the core Orca OS functionality for Ubuntu/Debian systems.
